  </fn>
  <fn fn-type="other" id="T2F4">
   <label>d</label>
   <p>The Se of air sampling was made conditional on a minimum prevalence of infected animals (incubation period) of 10%. For prevalences of &lt;10%, Se is 0.</p>
  </fn>
